# NSSpringLoadingHighlight.none

**Case**

A constant that indicates no highlighting.

## Declaration

```swift
case none
```

## Discussion

Don’t apply any highlighting style to the destination’s user interface. The destination is probably not spring-loadable.

## Constants

- **NSSpringLoadingHighlight.standard**: A constant that indicates standard highlighting to show the destination supports spring-loading.
- **NSSpringLoadingHighlight.emphasized**: A constant that indicates emphasized highlighting to show active spring-loading on the destination.
